title: Any one been sold a Google Pixel 5 phone with different IMEI1 numbers on phone & box? False Labeling
content: phoned where bought, 85 minutes on phone, promised call back from John Lewis, phoned again Not their problem? Promotion of free headphone at risk. 5 emails back from promotion before saying IMIE1 not the same! Is this False labelling common? Anyone else? Please check your box against *#06# or settings your phone.
